{
  "video_id": "iE9HMudybyc",
  "title": "Nilofer Merchant: Got a meeting? Take a walk",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13564.0,
      "end_time": 15335.0,
      "text": "What you're doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15335.0,
      "end_time": 18139.0,
      "text": "right now, at this very moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18139.0,
      "end_time": 20159.0,
      "text": "is killing you."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20159.0,
      "end_time": 22914.0,
      "text": "More than cars or the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22914.0,
      "end_time": 25683.0,
      "text": "or even that little mobile device we keep talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25683.0,
      "end_time": 28574.0,
      "text": "the technology you're using the most almost every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28574.0,
      "end_time": 31780.0,
      "text": "is this, your tush."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31780.0,
      "end_time": 34909.0,
      "text": "Nowadays people are sitting 9.3 hours a day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34909.0,
      "end_time": 38407.0,
      "text": "which is more than we're sleeping, at 7.7 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38407.0,
      "end_time": 40272.0,
      "text": "Sitting is so incredibly prevalent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40272.0,
      "end_time": 42249.0,
      "text": "we don't even question how much we're doing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42249.0,
      "end_time": 45191.0,
      "text": "and because everyone else is doing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45191.0,
      "end_time": 47965.0,
      "text": "it doesn't even occur to us that it's not okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47965.0,
      "end_time": 50277.0,
      "text": "In that way, sitting has become"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50277.0,
      "end_time": 54181.0,
      "text": "the smoking of our generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54181.0,
      "end_time": 56609.0,
      "text": "Of course there's health consequences to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56609.0,
      "end_time": 59390.0,
      "text": "scary ones, besides the waist."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59390.0,
      "end_time": 63042.0,
      "text": "Things like breast cancer and colon cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63042.0,
      "end_time": 66331.0,
      "text": "are directly tied to our lack of physical in activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66331.0,
      "end_time": 68963.0,
      "text": "Ten percent in fact, on both of those."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68963.0,
      "end_time": 70483.0,
      "text": "Six percent for heart disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70483.0,
      "end_time": 72506.0,
      "text": "seven percent for type 2 diabetes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72506.0,
      "end_time": 75286.0,
      "text": "which is what my father died of."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75286.0,
      "end_time": 77347.0,
      "text": "Now, any of those stats should convince each of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77347.0,
      "end_time": 78966.0,
      "text": "to get off our duff more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78966.0,
      "end_time": 81736.0,
      "text": "but if you're anything like me, it won't."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81736.0,
      "end_time": 84964.0,
      "text": "What did get me moving was a social interaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84964.0,
      "end_time": 86272.0,
      "text": "Someone invited me to a meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86272.0,
      "end_time": 87445.0,
      "text": "but couldn't manage to fit me in"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87445.0,
      "end_time": 90283.0,
      "text": "to a regular sort of conference room meeting, and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90283.0,
      "end_time": 94108.0,
      "text": "\"I have to walk my dogs tomorrow. Could you come then?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94108.0,
      "end_time": 96155.0,
      "text": "It seemed kind of odd to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96155.0,
      "end_time": 98265.0,
      "text": "and actually, that first meeting, I remember thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98265.0,
      "end_time": 100029.0,
      "text": "\"I have to be the one to ask the next question,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100029.0,
      "end_time": 103185.0,
      "text": "because I knew I was going to huff and puff"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103185.0,
      "end_time": 105369.0,
      "text": "during this conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105369.0,
      "end_time": 108499.0,
      "text": "And yet, I've taken that idea and made it my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108499.0,
      "end_time": 110145.0,
      "text": "So instead of going to coffee meetings"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110145.0,
      "end_time": 112373.0,
      "text": "or fluorescent-lit conference room meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112373.0,
      "end_time": 115403.0,
      "text": "I ask people to go on a walking meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 115403.0,
      "end_time": 119342.0,
      "text": "to the tune of 20 to 30 miles a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119342.0,
      "end_time": 121771.0,
      "text": "It's changed my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121771.0,
      "end_time": 125000.0,
      "text": "But before that, what actually happened was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125000.0,
      "end_time": 125982.0,
      "text": "I used to think about it as,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 125982.0,
      "end_time": 127678.0,
      "text": "you could take care of your health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127678.0,
      "end_time": 130202.0,
      "text": "or you could take care of obligations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 130202.0,
      "end_time": 134007.0,
      "text": "and one always came at the cost of the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 134007.0,
      "end_time": 137139.0,
      "text": "So now, several hundred of these walking meetings later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 137139.0,
      "end_time": 138512.0,
      "text": "I've learned a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138512.0,
      "end_time": 140386.0,
      "text": "First, there's this amazing thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140386.0,
      "end_time": 143111.0,
      "text": "about actually getting out of the box"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143111.0,
      "end_time": 145085.0,
      "text": "that leads to out-of-the-box thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145085.0,
      "end_time": 149510.0,
      "text": "Whether it's nature or the exercise itself, it certainly works."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 149510.0,
      "end_time": 152530.0,
      "text": "And second, and probably the more reflective one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 152530.0,
      "end_time": 154825.0,
      "text": "is just about how much each of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 154825.0,
      "end_time": 157289.0,
      "text": "can hold problems in opposition"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 157289.0,
      "end_time": 159264.0,
      "text": "when they're really not that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 159264.0,
      "end_time": 160972.0,
      "text": "And if we're going to solve problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160972.0,
      "end_time": 162570.0,
      "text": "and look at the world really differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162570.0,
      "end_time": 164699.0,
      "text": "whether it's in governance or business"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 164699.0,
      "end_time": 167561.0,
      "text": "or environmental issues, job creation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167561.0,
      "end_time": 170224.0,
      "text": "maybe we can think about how to reframe those problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 170224.0,
      "end_time": 172426.0,
      "text": "as having both things be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172426.0,
      "end_time": 174349.0,
      "text": "Because it was when that happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 174349.0,
      "end_time": 175804.0,
      "text": "with this walk-and-talk idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175804.0,
      "end_time": 179763.0,
      "text": "that things became doable and sustainable and viable."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 179763.0,
      "end_time": 181743.0,
      "text": "So I started this talk talking about the tush,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 181743.0,
      "end_time": 185753.0,
      "text": "so I'll end with the bottom line, which is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185753.0,
      "end_time": 187384.0,
      "text": "walk and talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 187384.0,
      "end_time": 188667.0,
      "text": "Walk the talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 188667.0,
      "end_time": 192335.0,
      "text": "You'll be surprised at how fresh air drives fresh thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192335.0,
      "end_time": 193931.0,
      "text": "and in the way that you do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193931.0,
      "end_time": 197459.0,
      "text": "you'll bring into your life an entirely new set of ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197459.0,
      "end_time": 199186.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 199186.0,
      "end_time": 209186.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}